analysis: You are very pleasant and come across as cooperative. You can be very spiritual and believe in higher powers. People see you as helpful.
You are full of boldness and confidence, with a tendency to freewheel. You portray yourself as straightforward and aggressive, and deeply want to become a leader.
You present yourself as a peacemaker, and can be very diplomatic. You tend to cooperate with anyone, and are very gently and polite.
You are very entertaining and can make anyone laugh; you are creative and always in a good mood. Your friendliness makes others think of you positively.
You are a hard worker and have a very strong work ethic. You're good at managing others and can execute tasks efficiently and with great attention to detail. People admire your sense of discipline.
You love to meet new people, and come across as extroverted. You prefer to be independent and free of responsibility.
You are very responsible and love your family and home. You have a lot of love to give to others and can function as a bit of a mom friend.

You have a lot of elegance and a more classic appeal. You can be very contained and tend to have your guard up when meeting new people. You are also very knowledgeable, but not necessarily outspoken about this.

You are very diligence and focused on hard work. You have an entrepreneurial spirit that matches your work ethic and makes it very possible for you to start your own business or follow through on other independent pursuits.

You have very humanitarian sensibilities and can be very charismatic. People see you as an intellectual, particularly one who is open-minded and has an ability to see things from others' perspectives.
